	<a name="installing"></a>
	<h3>
		<span class="glyph glyphicon glyphicon-star redFont" aria-hidden="true"></span>
		Instructions for installation
	</h3>
		<div class="text-center">
	<a  class="red-btn" href="/Website/Downloads/Other/z2t-Widget.msi"
			style="background-color: red;
			color: #fff;
			padding: 16px 16px;
			border-radius: 16px;
			font-weight: bold;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			font-size: 23px;
			text-shadow: 1px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.52);
			white-space: nowrap;">Download</a> <br><br>  
	</div>

	<p>
          <b>1)</b> If you have a version of this widget already installed, 
          please go to your control panel and uninstall it according to your computer's instructions.<br><br>
          
          <b>2)</b> Click the red &quot;Download&quot; button to download the Zip2Tax Widget
          installer.<br><br>
          
          <b>3)</b> The next step varies depending on what browser you are using:<br>
          
          <b>A)</b> <span class="firstword">Internet Explorer:</span> You will
          be asked to either &quot;Run&quot; or &quot;Save&quot; the program.  Click &quot;Run.&quot;<br>
          
          <b>B)</b> <span class="firstword">Mozilla Firefox:</span> A popup
          window will come up and you will be  asked to &quot;Save File.&quot;  Click &quot;Save
          File.&quot; Find the file and double-click it to run it.<br>
          
          <b>C)</b> <span class="firstword">Google Chrome:</span> The installer
          will automatically download. Find where the file has been saved and 
          double-click to run it.<br>
          <br>
          
          <b>4)</b> If you saved the installer file to your computer, double-click
          on it and run it.
          <br>
          <br>
          
          <b>5)</b> The installation window should pop up.<br>
          <br>
          
          <b>6)</b> Click &quot;Next&quot; to start the installation.<br>

		  <b>7)</b> Please read this end user license agreement carefully, and click on the "I agree" button and click "Next."<br>
		</p>
		
		<img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetLicenseAgreement.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax License Agreement"  class="img-responsive centered">          
          
        <p>  
          <b>8)</b> The installer automatically creates a folder on your computer
          to install the  Zip2Tax widget, but you can manually choose where it
          is saved. Usually it is  recommended that you leave it as is.<br>
          <br>
          
          <b>9)</b> Choose if this widget is just for you or for everyone who uses your computer.<br>
        </p>
        
	        <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetSelectInstallationFolder.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Select Installation Folder" class="img-responsive centered">        
        <p>
          <b>10)</b> Click the &quot;Next&quot; button to start the installation.<br>
        </p>
          
	        <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetConfirmInstallation.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Confirm Installation" class="img-responsive centered">

		<p>
          <b>11)</b> Installing the widget may take a few minutes, so just wait until it is finished.<br>
        </p>
        
	        <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetInstallingScreen.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Being Installed" class="img-responsive centered">
        
        <p>  
          <b>12)</b> Click the &quot;Close&quot; button once the installation is finished.<br>
        </p>
        
	        <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetInstallationComplete.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Installation Complete" class="img-responsive centered">
