	<a name="use_widget"></a>
	<h3>
		<span class="glyph glyphicon glyphicon-star redFont" aria-hidden="true"></span>
		How to use the Zip2Tax widget
	</h3>

		<p>
          <b>1)</b> After you install the widget, there should be a shortcut icon on your desktop that
          looks like the image below:<br>
        </p>
          
	      <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetDesktopIcon.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Widget Shortcut Icon" class="img-responsive centered">
        
        <p>  
          <b>2)</b> To run the widget program, double-click on the shortcut.<br>
        </p>
        
        <p>  
          <b>3)</b> A small window may pop up that asks you if you want to run this file. Click &quot;Yes&quot;.<br>
        </p>
		
	      <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/DoYouWantToRunThisFile.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Run This File?" class="img-responsive centered">
          
         <p>  
          <b>4)</b> A small window should pop up that asks for your username and password.<br>
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <b>5)</b> Enter your unique username and password and click on the &quot;Login&quot; button.<br>
        </p>
        
	      <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetLogin.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Widget Login Window" class="img-responsive centered">
        
        <p>
          <b>6)</b> Once you've logged in, you can enter in a ZIP code and click &quot;Get Rate!&quot;<br>
        </p>
        
	      <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetGetRateWindow.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Widget Enter ZIP Code Window"  class="img-responsive centered">          
        
        <p>  
          <b>7)</b> The example below entered in the ZIP code &quot;90601&quot; for Whittier, CA.<br>
        </p>
        
	      <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetEnterZIPCode.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Widget ZIP Code Info"  class="img-responsive centered">          
        
        <p>
          <b>8)</b> Click on the &quot;Show Details&quot; button to get specifics on that particular ZIP code.<br>
        </p>

		<img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetGetDetails.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Widget Enter ZIP Code Window"  class="img-responsive centered">          
        
        <p>  
          <b>9)</b> You can enter in a specific dollar amount and click &quot;Calculate.&quot; The program calculates sales 
          tax and total sales for you.<br>
        </p>
          
	      <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetGetDetailsAmount.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Widget Dollar Amount"  class="img-responsive centered">          
        
        <p>  
          <b>10)</b> You can also view details of communities using the same ZIP code by clicking on the choices 
          at the bottom of the window under the section called &quot;Other Communities Using 90601.&quot;<br>
        </p>
		
		<p>  
          <b>11)</b> Click on "My Account" to go to the Zip2Tax web site or click on "Get Help" to contact us.<br>
        </p>
          
	      <img src="/Website/images/widget/NewImages/WidgetGetDetailsOtherCommunities.jpg" alt="Screenshot: Zip2Tax Widget Other Communities"  class="img-responsive centered">
		  
